     * * Write a Java function to count the number of prime numbers less than a given non-negative number.
     *
     * > countPrimesNums(5)
     * 2
     * > countPrimesNums(10)
     * 4
     * > countPrimesNums(100)
     * 25
     */
    public static int countPrimesNums(int n) {
