class FindRemainder {
    /**
     * * Write a Java function to find remainder of array multiplication divided by n.
     *
     * > findRemainder([100, 10, 5, 25, 35, 14], 6, 11)
     * 9
     * > findRemainder([1, 1, 1], 3, 1)
     * 0
     * > findRemainder([1, 2, 1], 3, 2)
